21
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:30,800
The circles of us young people and the elders

22
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,200
are different after all.

23
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:37,960
Well, I

24
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:40,600
prefer to control the direction of the boat myself.

25
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:41,560
Oh no,

26
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,400
