27
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,259
Come on, just sit with Xiao Chuan.

28
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,640
Make the most of this opportunity.

29
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,520
Go ahead.

30
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,800
