87
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:39,880
I remember you've always loved Suzhou silk.

88
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:43,240
Tomorrow, I'll go to Suzhou to get more for your dowry.

89
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,280
